RHINFO command
Form:           RHINFO  "kill/s"
Purpose:        To give information about the ring handler
Author:         BJK
Specification:
        Gives information about number of basic blocks with bad checksums,
    basic blocks recieved and unwanted, information about blocks recieved,
    and information about allocated ports.
        If the switch 'kill' is quoted the ring handler will be removed if
    possible.


